<br>
In Hibernia, the dampwood mites(lvl 24is) near Innis are nice money makers. Drop coin only. 10-15g an hour. <br>
<br>
Anything like that in Midgard? I know the mobs on the frontier drop coin, but wondering if anything in the actual realm is like this. <br>
